Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(2018年8月某日)\N-我是第一次 -那就自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(东京某宾馆)\N声音很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,(和麻里进行摄影前的商讨)\N-你是导演 -差不多是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要出外景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(今天导演不在 我来进行拍摄)\N-出去玩 -去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有别人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,自由行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,先是这样打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,先问下大家的意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次拍这种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,会大概商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有让大家看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是之前 -好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是哪里啊 -这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去了游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实这是第一弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就是出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让大家开开心心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-想要去冲绳\N-麻里想去冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(想要去冲绳)\N真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才说了规则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(随便玩但是全部都要播出来)\N-都要播出吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是已经拍过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（2018年1月12日发售麻里内射）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,之前拍过吧 真的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,特别舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(和麻里做爱让男优忘记工作)\N真的爽的忘记是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,带不带套感觉不一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-不戴比较舒服 -舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢不戴套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子不轻易说 但就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-是这样\N-这次有规则要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,(5条规则\N1.开心拍摄 2.认真拍摄)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(3.全部内射 4.不拍摄不能做\N5.麻里做主)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在不拍摄的时候做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的 -好像你已经做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-还要很开心\N-是的 还要本人同意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在拍就是可以做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要经过同意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在说明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以坐下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其实的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在交流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好像很难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要有气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里很不好做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道了 -什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在先要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,亲一亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你看在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-要开始了\N-感觉今天很难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-很难办吧 -好滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这样的内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢这样的内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢蓝色的内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是丁字裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,感动什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的情绪真的很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样的白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-来摸摸看\N-直接开始了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,里面太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,进去里面很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,里面舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股撅起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以直接插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才已经进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的太紧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,换人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自己握住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没套的肉棒舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来换人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把奶子露出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家排队来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要按顺序啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以握住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用上手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好好握住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,自己夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有进去
