Dialogue: 0,2:41:46.68,2:41:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:41:51.82,2:41:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:42:02.10,2:42:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:42:40.27,2:42:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:15.87,2:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:43:41.93,2:43:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:44:07.99,2:44:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:44:15.33,2:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: 0,2:44:46.16,2:44:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:45:23.96,2:45:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:45:40.85,2:45:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,2:45:50.02,2:45:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:45:59.93,2:46:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:46:42.88,2:46:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-想高潮吗？ -给我
Dialogue: 0,2:47:59.22,2:48:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:48:11.33,2:48:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:49:13.36,2:49:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:49:39.05,2:49:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我啊
Dialogue: 0,2:50:05.11,2:50:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,2:50:22.00,2:50:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:50:37.78,2:50:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:50:55.40,2:50:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:51:15.95,2:51:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,继续给我啊
Dialogue: 0,2:52:44.04,2:52:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在动呢
Dialogue: 0,2:52:48.07,2:52:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:53:26.25,2:53:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:53:37.26,2:53:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:53:50.84,2:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,自己放
Dialogue: 0,2:54:15.80,2:54:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看镜头
Dialogue: 0,2:54:24.24,2:54:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:55:09.02,2:55:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要到了
Dialogue: 0,2:55:27.73,2:55:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:57:15.64,2:57:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:57:41.33,2:57:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:57:43.54,2:57:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-还要吗？ -给我
Dialogue: 0,2:57:58.58,2:58:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:58:10.33,2:58:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,2:58:33.09,2:58:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:59:01.35,2:59:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:59:05.38,2:59:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,2:59:07.59,2:59:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在害羞了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:59:16.03,2:59:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-麻里 -好害羞
Dialogue: 0,2:59:21.17,2:59:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大家在担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:59:23.37,2:59:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,2:59:26.67,2:59:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来了好多电话啊
Dialogue: 0,2:59:34.01,2:59:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我打回去撒一下谎啊
Dialogue: 0,2:59:38.78,2:59:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说你不舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:59:45.76,2:59:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才麻里身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:59:53.47,2:59:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没事了 马上回去
Dialogue: 0,3:00:00.07,3:00:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才想要叫你们的
Dialogue: 0,3:00:03.74,3:00:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是太快了
Dialogue: 0,3:00:06.68,3:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有听到手机响
Dialogue: 0,3:00:13.65,3:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里很健康的
Dialogue: 0,3:00:17.32,3:00:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,3:00:18.79,3:00:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了 马上回去
Dialogue: 0,3:00:25.03,3:00:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我挂了
Dialogue: 0,3:00:34.94,3:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(晚上10点5分)\N来电话了吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:00:40.08,3:00:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,马上过来了
Dialogue: 0,3:00:44.12,3:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,(杉山的家里)
Dialogue: 0,3:00:54.03,3:01:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(在等待小田切的到来)
Dialogue: 0,3:01:01.37,3:01:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,3:01:05.77,3:01:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,3:01:10.54,3:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:18.62,3:01:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要到时间了 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,3:01:25.59,3:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:27.79,3:01:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-太好了 -身体没事吧
Dialogue: 0,3:01:32.57,3:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-感觉没事啊 -现在好了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:38.44,3:01:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经快没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:45.41,3:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是有限制的
Dialogue: 0,3:01:48.71,3:01:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不好 去休息了一下
Dialogue: 0,3:01:52.39,3:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(被抱怨的小田切)\N-说一声 -你们走的太快
Dialogue: 0,3:01:58.62,3:02:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们走的很慢\N-她已经不能走了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:05.23,3:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,3:02:07.80,3:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(先来干杯) 今天辛苦了\N还有点时间 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:14.04,3:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,3:02:22.11,3:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,两天时间过的很快啊
Dialogue: 0,3:02:27.99,3:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是48小时
Dialogue: 0,3:02:32.76,3:02:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,3:02:38.26,3:02:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,3:02:40.83,3:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,3:02:42.67,3:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面感觉印象\N不一样的人有吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:02:49.28,3:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-大家都是 -是吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:02:53.31,3:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是变好了还是差了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:56.62,3:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个很重要 -变好了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:02.49,3:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:05.06,3:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不能中止其实很担心
Dialogue: 0,3:03:13.87,3:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:19.74,3:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:03:24.51,3:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了 已经喝完了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:29.65,3:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个还有 -已经凉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:03:37.72,3:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以打开吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:03:42.50,3:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要做吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:03:43.96,3:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心灯啊
Dialogue: 0,3:03:48.00,3:03:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,3:03:50.20,3:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们保险
Dialogue: 0,3:03:53.14,3:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:03:56.81,3:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,3:04:02.31,3:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,3:04:08.55,3:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吗
Dialogue: 0,3:04:12.59,3:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,3:04:17.73,3:04:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,3:04:25.80,3:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,3:04:27.64,3:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,3:04:29.11,3:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,3:04:34.25,3:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,3:04:43.79,3:04:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多长时间
Dialogue: 0,3:04:48.93,3:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两个多小时啊
Dialogue: 0,3:05:00.67,3:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 -不要问
Dialogue: 0,3:05:03.61,3:05:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什麽可怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,3:05:08.38,3:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麽 是礼物吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:05:13.52,3:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给大家的礼物吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:05:19.02,3:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,3:05:25.63,3:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的兴趣 我拿来了
Dialogue: 0,3:05:34.07,3:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想要麻里穿上
Dialogue: 0,3:05:37.38,3:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,3:05:41.05,3:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们能理解
Dialogue: 0,3:05:45.45,3:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-好可怕 -知道了
Dialogue: 0,3:05:53.16,3:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这个吧
Dialogue: 0,3:05:56.10,3:06:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:02.33,3:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-好厉害 -是丝袜吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:06:07.11,3:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是腿啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:08.94,3:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是这样的
Dialogue: 0,3:06:17.02,3:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,3:06:19.22,3:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-要都脱了吗？-是的
Dialogue: 0,3:06:24.72,3:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很不龤啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:28.39,3:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:31.70,3:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:35.00,3:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,身材真好啊
Dialogue: 0,3:06:39.04,3:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-给你这个 -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,3:06:43.44,3:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:06:46.01,3:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要把内裤脱掉
Dialogue: 0,3:06:54.09,3:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,3:06:59.59,3:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,3:07:01.43,3:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我 -不要这样
Dialogue: 0,3:07:08.40,3:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:07:14.64,3:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,3:07:17.21,3:07:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的很适合你啊 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,3:07:25.65,3:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是在哪里买的啊
Dialogue: 0,3:07:29.69,3:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在专卖店
Dialogue: 0,3:07:33.36,3:07:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,专门去买的
Dialogue: 0,3:07:50.61,3:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,3:07:56.12,3:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,3:08:06.02,3:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,3:08:08.23,3:08:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,3:08:16.67,3:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要来检查一下
Dialogue: 0,3:08:21.44,3:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-有什么东西吗？-没有
Dialogue: 0,3:08:27.31,3:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要看好好穿上了吗
Dialogue: 0,3:08:31.72,3:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样感受一下
Dialogue: 0,3:08:37.96,3:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什么检查啊
Dialogue: 0,3:08:39.79,3:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要看看是不是合身
Dialogue: 0,3:08:48.97,3:08:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,3:08:52.27,3:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-没事 -没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:08:55.57,3:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你变态啊
Dialogue: 0,3:08:58.14,3:09:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-没事 -印象变了
Dialogue: 0,3:09:01.08,3:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,3:09:06.22,3:09:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样可以吗？-还不错
Dialogue: 0,3:09:10.62,3:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-很合身 -那太好了
Dialogue: 0,3:09:15.39,3:09:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已经穿好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:09:20.53,3:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来看看
Dialogue: 0,3:09:24.57,3:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,3:09:26.41,3:09:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,3:09:28.24,3:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:09:34.11,3:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,3:09:35.95,3:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样被看的
Dialogue: 0,3:09:39.62,3:09:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不错啊
Dialogue: 0,3:09:43.29,3:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下后面 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,3:09:49.53,3:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摆一下性感的姿势吗？
Dialogue: 0,3:09:55.03,3:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老师来指导一下
Dialogue: 0,3:10:07.51,3:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 腿很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,3:10:14.12,3:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,都能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,3:10:18.16,3:10:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,3:10:22.93,3:10:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是绝景啊
Dialogue: 0,3:10:28.07,3:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,3:10:32.10,3:10:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不一样了
Dialogue: 0,3:10:35.41,3:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把手抬起来腿绕一起
Dialogue: 0,3:10:41.65,3:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
