Dialogue: 0,3:10:52.29,3:10:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 很好
Dialogue: 0,3:10:58.53,3:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,位置不对啊
Dialogue: 0,3:11:04.04,3:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,3:11:06.97,3:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下 -我看一下角度
Dialogue: 0,3:11:15.05,3:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,3:11:20.92,3:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
